{"id": "4743273", "title": "Nano-X Imaging: Expanded FDA Clearance Paves The Path For Deployment", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Normal pediatric chest x-ray\" data-id=\"869557690\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"855px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">radiologist/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Nano-X Imaging (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NNOX\" title=\"Nano-X Imaging Ltd.\">NNOX</a></span>) is quite a stock enigma. Every few quarters, the shares of NNOX race higher on some positive news, only to see most of the gains dissipate over the following months.</p> <p>For example, back in March, NNOX shares more than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743273-nano-x-imaging-expanded-fda-clearance-paves-the-path-for-deployment", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:45:46"}, {"id": "4743268", "title": "Skye Bioscience: Nimacimab Targets Safer Weight Loss, Speculative Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Unrecognizable Black Lady Showing Abdominal Muscles Wearing Oversized Jeans Indoor\" data-id=\"1467665258\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Prostock-Studio</p></figcaptio